Instead of taking that monthly donation...

23:58.979 --> 24:01.273
fucking take whatever
they don't want us to have.

24:08.155 --> 24:09.823
[pounds on the desk]

24:14.035 --> 24:15.287
Let's see if you're right.

24:20.292 --> 24:22.627
[narrator] You wanna know
how fucked up Mexico is?

24:22.711 --> 24:25.046
