the right commander to come on duty.

24:31.219 --> 24:32.762
-[in Spanish] How's it going?
-Hey.

24:32.971 --> 24:34.681
-Good luck!
-Thank you.

24:34.806 --> 24:36.183
Hey, guys.

24:38.101 --> 24:39.686
[narrator]
