to make sense, but not give it all away.

24:44.441 --> 24:47.152
The trucks will be rolling heavy
and we can hit them easy.

24:47.694 --> 24:49.988
It'd be a solid bust for you with the DF.

24:50.071 --> 24:52.282
Real nice opportunity for you
and your boys.

24:52.657 --> 24:57.746
[narrator] "Opportunity" being MFJP code
for "a chance to score off the seizure."

24:58.246 --> 25:02.667
It was truly an art, wrangling
federales into just doing their jobs.

25:07.422 --> 25:08.340
POLICE

25:08.423 --> 25:10.217
[chatter over radio in Spanish]

25:11.176 --> 25:13.303
[in Spanish]
Nobody in front of me, gentlemen.

25:13.929 --> 25:15.722
-Got it?
-Yes, got it.

25:17.682 --> 25:20.769
[in English] I'd get to those trucks
as fast as you fucking can.

25:30.779 --> 25:32.697
[tires squeal]

25:39.788 --> 25:43.041
[man speaking over loudspeaker in Spanish]

25:43.124 --> 25:45.502
[officer in Spanish]
Don't move, motherfucker! Don't move!

25:45.585 --> 25:48.588
[men shouting in Spanish]

25:51.967 --> 25:54.094
Hey! On the ground!

25:54.427 --> 25:55.637
Down!

26:00.225 --> 26:01.268
[toilet flushes]

26:02.060 --> 26:02.894
[grunts]

26:03.853 --> 26:05.355
[in English]
Keep going. Keep going.

26:24.457 --> 26:27.502
[in Spanish]
Down! On the ground!

26:28.378 --> 26:29.212
[man] Clear!

26:30.797 --> 26:32.924
-Police!
-Drop your weapons.

26:34.384 --> 26:36.177
Lower your guns. Search the place.

26:47.063 --> 26:49.941
-[Kiki in English] I need a bolt cutter.
-Let's get him some bolt cutters.

26:50.942 --> 26:51.776
[man 2] Let's do it.

27:05.373 --> 27:07.417
[men murmuring]

27:18.136 --> 27:19.554
[Kiki] Fuck.

27:25.435 --> 27:26.728
[in Spanish]
Round up everyone.

27:26.811 --> 27:29.773
