27:41.284 --> 27:42.285
Let's go.

27:43.244 --> 27:45.955
[in English] Well, damn, Kiki.
I think he likes you.

27:49.918 --> 27:52.295
He's mad
because he had to do his fucking job.

27:52.379 --> 27:53.713
This place is dirty as fuck.

27:53.797 --> 27:54.839
Hey, man...

27:56.591 --> 27:57.967
