27:58.593 --> 28:02.055
Sir, if there's nothing to it,
then why is he guarding this place with--

28:02.138 --> 28:04.516
Because this pipe's expensive
and they'll steal anything here.

28:05.183 --> 28:07.977
But you don't know that
because you're new and you're pressing.

28:08.895 --> 28:11.773
I know you came here to make cases,
but it ain't gonna happen in a day.

28:13.149 --> 28:14.234
Let's go.

28:28.373 --> 28:29.916
[in Spanish]
Fucking drill.

28:34.838 --> 28:37.173
[ax clanging]

28:40.802 --> 28:42.637
[grunting]

28:55.150 --> 28:56.109
TIJUANA, BAJA CALIFORNIA

28:56.192 --> 28:58.236
[Gabriel Allende's
"Yuiria de Mis Amores" playing]

29:06.870 --> 29:08.621
-[in Spanish] Is it here?
-Yeah, here.

29:09.080 --> 29:10.165
[horn honks]

29:18.047 --> 29:20.133
-[Félix] There he is.
-Yeah.

29:21.718 --> 29:22.927
[Félix]
What's up, Benjamín?

29:23.595 --> 29:24.429
How's it going?

29:25.180 --> 29:26.639
Miguel Ángel. Gentlemen.

29:28.349 --> 29:30.602
-You just gonna sit here or what?
-No, let's go.

29:33.605 --> 29:35.648
[Félix]
Looks like you don't miss Culiacán.

29:35.732 --> 29:36.983
"El otro lado" is 3 blocks away.

29:37.066 --> 29:39.194
Any asshole with a truck
can make good money.

29:39.694 --> 29:41.529
-Electronics?
-Yeah.

29:41.863 --> 29:45.116
Japanese shit. Designer jeans.
