35:40.805 --> 35:42.849
[chuckles] Asshole!

35:44.058 --> 35:45.935
[man shouts]

35:46.894 --> 35:48.104
[chattering]

35:49.939 --> 35:51.566
[sighs]

35:55.653 --> 35:56.654
Uncle!

35:58.823 --> 36:00.366
[man shouts]

36:00.741 --> 36:04.370
-What's up with those Chinese fuckers?
-They're going to fuck each other up.

36:04.453 --> 36:05.913
[man shouts]

36:05.997 --> 36:08.416
♪ Or the things
That you say that you'll do ♪

36:08.499 --> 36:09.834
-[snorts]
-♪ Hold the line... ♪

36:09.917 --> 36:10.751
[man shouts]

36:10.835 --> 36:12.753
What a fucking party, man.

36:14.005 --> 36:14.839
Holy shit!

36:15.715 --> 36:18.134
[Félix]
It's a different business than yours.

36:18.718 --> 36:20.428
We won't be in competition with you.

36:20.845 --> 36:22.305
Now that's a relief.

36:27.852 --> 36:29.187
It's good for everyone.

36:29.812 --> 36:31.314
One single organization...

36:31.939 --> 36:35.776
that would control all the cultivation
and distribution of marijuana in Mexico,

36:35.860 --> 36:38.029
which means less violence...

36:38.779 --> 36:39.989
less bullshit.

36:40.072 --> 36:44.243
I give you my word,
this won't interfere with your business.

36:44.619 --> 36:46.913
We'll be the perfect neighbors.

36:50.166 --> 36:53.294
Isabella's right, as usual.
You are a serious man.

36:53.753 --> 36:55.880
You have my consent, Mr. Félix.

36:57.632 --> 36:59.091
Welcome to Tijuana.

36:59.175 --> 37:00.718
[chuckles] Well, thank you.

37:02.470 --> 37:05.514
