let alone Sinaloans, getting organized...

37:10.436 --> 37:13.814
seems unlikely. No offense.

37:13.898 --> 37:15.358
[chuckles]

37:15.441 --> 37:16.275
Yeah.

37:16.859 --> 37:20.196
Just give me some time
and I'll change your mind.

37:22.448 --> 37:24.784
You have
a lot of work ahead of you, friend.

37:24.867 --> 37:26.994
Hmm? A lot.

37:27.411 --> 37:29.288
A lot. Enjoy the party.

37:30.873 --> 37:33.668
[Mariachi music playing]

37:43.970 --> 37:45.930
