37:54.605 --> 37:57.525
We're a long way from Sinaloa. Both of us.

38:00.486 --> 38:02.446
Isabella, wait.

38:06.367 --> 38:08.160
Mmm.

38:08.244 --> 38:11.289
I forgot you're
the last decent man in Mexico.

38:11.372 --> 38:12.373
[chuckles]

38:12.456 --> 38:14.417
Let's hope not.

38:16.002 --> 38:17.712
I want to make some real money.

38:20.673 --> 38:23.342
Thank you for your help.
I won't forget it.

38:23.968 --> 38:25.136
Miguel Ángel...

38:26.095 --> 38:31.100
if you can make this work, trust me,
I won't let you forget.

38:43.904 --> 38:46.949
-[in English] You're up early.
-Oh, I couldn't sleep.

39:01.964 --> 39:04.133
Thought you said there was nothing
in those trucks.

39:05.217 --> 39:06.635
[sighs]

39:10.848 --> 39:12.350
Just don't piss anyone off.

39:13.476 --> 39:15.728
Well, that's what I do.

39:18.773 --> 39:19.982
I'll check in later.

39:38.959 --> 39:40.795
[whirring]

39:57.853 --> 39:59.772
[in Spanish]
Just a little help for tonight.

40:35.099 --> 40:37.601
