40:59.290 --> 41:00.958
[Rafa whispers]
Sons of bitches.

41:28.068 --> 41:30.112
-[grunts]
-[howling from a distance]

41:34.158 --> 41:35.659
What the fuck, Rafa?

41:39.580 --> 41:41.499
[men murmuring]

41:41.582 --> 41:43.459
You fucking kidding, Rafa?

41:45.294 --> 41:46.587
You've lost your mind.

41:48.297 --> 41:50.466
Rafa, chill the fuck out.

41:53.344 --> 41:54.845
God damn it.

41:57.223 --> 41:59.600
Rafa, you're going to kill us all.

42:04.355 --> 42:08.651
[loud explosions]

42:22.998 --> 42:24.583
[rumbling]

42:28.462 --> 42:31.340
-No fucking way! No fucking way, dude!
-[cheering]

42:32.341 --> 42:34.260
-No fucking way, dude!
-[laughs]

42:44.395 --> 42:46.355
[Maria]
The little sneak hides the candy.

42:46.438 --> 42:47.731
[knock on door]

42:47.815 --> 42:50.359
She found a stash in the laundry basket.

42:52.111 --> 42:54.363
That little cheat. Just like her mom.

42:54.905 --> 42:56.657
Hold on, honey.

43:00.452 --> 43:02.288
The DFS is downstairs.

43:02.955 --> 43:04.498
And the boss is here.

43:11.213 --> 43:13.007
-I have to go, Maria.
-Miguel.

43:13.090 --> 43:14.800
Avilés will listen to you.

43:15.509 --> 43:19.263
Long as you tell him
what he wants to hear.

43:20.014 --> 43:22.266
Yeah, talk to you later.

43:22.600 --> 43:24.310
Kiss the babies for me.

43:28.772 --> 43:30.983
[vehicle approaching]

44:01.305 --> 44:04.725
Neto says you got these motherfuckers
to agree to this thing.

44:04.808 --> 44:08.520
That's right.
They agreed to show up at least.

44:12.650 --> 44:15.444
Truth is,
I never thought this shit would work.

44:16.195 --> 44:18.864
-Yeah.
-But here we are.

44:21.617 --> 44:26.497
Sir, there's one last thing to handle
in order for this to work.

44:28.165 --> 44:30.209
You need to make amends with Pablo Acosta.

44:34.880 --> 44:36.256
I have to do what?

44:38.884 --> 44:40.928
What the fuck are you talking about?

44:42.054 --> 44:45.474
I know it's difficult but...
it's the only way.

44:47.142 --> 44:48.560
Just this last thing.

44:49.478 --> 44:53.399
Once it's done, you'll control the largest
marijuana organization in Mexico.

44:53.691 --> 44:56.110
Not just Mexico. In the entire world.

44:57.945 --> 44:59.822
I knew this was a dumb idea.

45:00.948 --> 45:01.990
Sir.

45:02.908 --> 45:06.578
You just shake his hand,
say a couple of words and it's done.

45:07.496 --> 45:10.791
And in return,
Acosta has to show you respect.

45:10.874 --> 45:12.292
They all do.

45:16.338 --> 45:17.923
They'll work for you.

45:20.884 --> 45:23.679
You'll be king, Don Pedro.

45:33.814 --> 45:35.566
I'll smooth things over with Acosta.

45:37.943 --> 45:39.153
Thank you, sir.

45:40.904 --> 45:42.781
I'll wait for you downstairs.

45:45.159 --> 45:46.285
What's up, boys?

45:47.202 --> 45:48.454
[chuckles]

45:49.788 --> 45:51.790
[sighs]

45:58.046 --> 46:00.799
[ballad playing]

46:02.176 --> 46:04.052
[radio crackling]

46:08.432 --> 46:09.391
[mouths] Fuck that.

46:15.689 --> 46:16.523
[unzips zipper]

46:18.317 --> 46:19.943
[urinating]

46:24.782 --> 46:28.535
So then, gentlemen, we are guaranteeing
protection for all your plazas.

46:29.244 --> 46:33.749
With the agreement of every man here,
my boss, Pedro Avilés of Sinaloa,

46:34.249 --> 46:38.879
Pablo Acosta of Ojinaga,
the Arellano Félix brothers from Tijuana,

46:39.254 --> 46:44.593
our friend Gabino Salcido from Mazatlán,
Filemón Medina of Zacatecas,

46:44.676 --> 46:46.595
Rene Verdugo from Nogales.

46:46.678 --> 46:50.974
And of course the DFS, which will
coordinate security for our arrangement.

46:51.058 --> 46:53.685
Today is an important day for all of us.

46:55.938 --> 46:57.898
Gentlemen, we have our consortium.

46:58.649 --> 47:01.360
Cheers!

47:01.443 --> 47:03.153
[applause]

47:08.534 --> 47:09.368
[Pablo] Gentlemen...

47:11.286 --> 47:14.957
this is a proud day to be Mexican.

47:16.959 --> 47:20.838
I want to toast to the man
who made this possible...

47:21.797 --> 47:24.424
brought us all together...

47:24.842 --> 47:28.554
Miguel Ángel Félix Gallardo,
our brother from Sinaloa. Cheers.

47:28.637 --> 47:30.597
[all] Cheers!

47:30.681 --> 47:33.308
[Félix] And I would like to say
that none of this could happen...

47:33.392 --> 47:37.896
without the leadership of Pedro Avilés.

47:39.189 --> 47:42.401
We owe you a lot. Thank you, Boss.
Thank you!

47:42.651 --> 47:44.903
[all] Bravo!

47:46.738 --> 47:48.574
I have something to add.

47:49.700 --> 47:52.870
I'm happy to proceed
with this fine arrangement.

47:54.329 --> 47:56.665
With one small modification.

47:57.875 --> 48:01.837
I've made it a practice in my life,
and in my work...

48:02.754 --> 48:06.300
never... to work with a lying cocksucker.

48:08.719 --> 48:10.804
So that means Pablo Acosta is out.

48:11.763 --> 48:13.390
You hear me, motherfucker?

48:14.266 --> 48:16.518
Get the fuck out of my consortium.

48:20.814 --> 48:24.735
Boss, with all due respect,
without Juárez, there's no agreement.

48:26.194 --> 48:28.614
[Benjamín] If Juárez's going
to be undercutting our price...

48:29.239 --> 48:30.532
my family's not interested.

48:31.867 --> 48:32.868
Let's go.

48:32.951 --> 48:35.829
[Avilés] Get the fuck out.
We don't need you.

48:57.434 --> 48:58.518
[Pablo] Let's go.

49:00.979 --> 49:01.980
[sighs]

49:07.527 --> 49:10.530
You're coming back to Sinaloa
with me tonight, Miguelito.

49:12.658 --> 49:15.702
I don't think city life
agrees with you, son.

49:30.759 --> 49:32.552
[engine sputtering]

49:53.782 --> 49:54.616
[in English] Fuck.

50:00.414 --> 50:01.790
[grunts]

50:55.302 --> 50:57.220
-[in Spanish] Ready?
-[Amado] Fuck this.

50:58.221 --> 51:01.224
Say the word, bro. We have guns too.

51:03.518 --> 51:04.561
No.

51:05.812 --> 51:07.314
Thanks for everything, Amado.

51:09.649 --> 51:11.359
Take care of yourself, Don Neto.

51:12.486 --> 51:13.737
Do me a favor.

51:17.532 --> 51:19.117
Get this to my wife.

51:19.618 --> 51:20.827
You got it.

51:22.537 --> 51:24.581
It was a beautiful idea, Miguel Ángel.

51:26.166 --> 51:28.210
What the fuck is happening? Let's go!

51:41.932 --> 51:43.183
Get in the back.

51:51.733 --> 51:52.984
Come by my place tomorrow.

51:53.485 --> 51:54.778
You got it, Pedro.

51:56.238 --> 51:57.405
[Avilés] Let's go.

52:07.374 --> 52:11.253
Just tell my wife and my son
where I'm buried.

52:11.837 --> 52:14.673
So the little son of a bitch
can catch up with me in ten years?

52:16.007 --> 52:17.384
No, thanks.

52:19.719 --> 52:20.554
Look.

52:21.179 --> 52:23.807
Sometimes, it's better to know your place.

52:25.308 --> 52:27.102
To just stay the fuck put.

52:31.481 --> 52:32.816
[sirens blare]

52:35.360 --> 52:36.361
[Avilés]
You kidding me?

52:58.592 --> 53:02.012
[Avilés] Fucking pigs.
Five hundred should do it.

53:04.681 --> 53:06.099
Identification.

53:08.435 --> 53:10.896
Call your boss if you want to know
who I am, asshole.

53:11.396 --> 53:12.689
You. Hands on the wheel.

53:13.148 --> 53:14.941
Hands on the wheel.

53:15.025 --> 53:18.486
Get out of the car.
The three of you as well. Come on!

53:20.572 --> 53:22.866
[Avilés]
You guys are making a mistake.

53:30.665 --> 53:33.084
How many mouths am I feeding tonight?

53:45.055 --> 53:46.556
Hey! What the fuck!

53:48.266 --> 53:49.351
Neto!

53:49.976 --> 53:52.270
What the hell! What's going on?

54:07.494 --> 54:09.496
I heard enough before I left.

54:10.789 --> 54:12.082
And...

54:12.958 --> 54:14.334
your friend...

54:15.001 --> 54:17.254
tells me he can't do it without you.

54:19.214 --> 54:21.883
[grunts]

54:24.135 --> 54:25.428
No, wait.

54:25.512 --> 54:27.347
[panting]

54:28.431 --> 54:29.599
Please.

54:40.068 --> 54:41.194
Boss.

55:09.639 --> 55:11.099
Grab the driver.

55:12.642 --> 55:15.061
Get out, motherfucker. Come on!

55:28.450 --> 55:29.826
You're from La Tuna, right?

55:32.746 --> 55:33.830
Your name?

55:34.664 --> 55:37.417
-Joaquín.
-We have a bunch of Joaquíns.

55:39.627 --> 55:40.879
What else do they call you?

55:43.173 --> 55:44.174
Chapo.

55:48.178 --> 55:50.013
You want to work for me?

55:52.891 --> 55:54.017
Okay, Chapo.

56:05.570 --> 56:07.447
You and I are partners now.

56:08.990 --> 56:10.492
You know what that means?

56:11.117 --> 56:12.077
Yes.

56:15.038 --> 56:16.164
Let's go.

56:23.129 --> 56:26.383
-Still driving you to Sinaloa?
-No.

56:28.593 --> 56:30.261
We're going back to Guadalajara.

56:36.351 --> 56:37.852
[birds chirping]

56:54.202 --> 56:55.995
[vehicle approaching]
